nodeMetric.field_example:
If a customer subscribes to a service with a 1-year renewal agreement for $12,000, then Annual Recurring Revenue would be;
ARR = $12,000

If a customer subscribes to a service for $10,000 (with no contract), then Annual Recurring Revenue would be;
ARR = $0

If a customer subscribes to a service with a monthly renewal agreement for $1,000 per month, then Annual Recurring Revenue would be;
ARR = $1,000 * 12 = $12,000
